description: This skill reports the air quality index for US zip codes.  The data is sourced from the U.S. EPA AirNow program.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask air quality to get me the report for 07753
Alexa, ask air quality for the forecast for 07753
Alexa, ask air quality what's the forecast for 07753
name: Air Quality
shortDescription: This skill reports the air quality index for US zip codes
